/*********************************************/
		MODULE INFORMATION
/*********************************************/

	Module for adding the NC State Branding Bar to the top of your Drupal
	website or as a block in a selected region.
	
	This plugin has been tested in Drupal 6.x.


/*********************************************/
		CREATED BY
/*********************************************/

	Plugin provided by NC State University Office of Information Technology
	
	Design, Education & Outreach
	http://oitdesign.ncsu.edu
	@oitdesign

/*********************************************/
        MANUAL INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
/*********************************************/

	 1. Download the package from http://drupal.ncsu.edu/features
	 
	 2. Copy to directory in <drupal site root>/sites/all/modules/ncstatebrandingbar
	 	(so that this readme's path is: 
	 	<drupal site root>/sites/all/modules/ncstatebrandingbar/readme)
	 
	 3. Enable in Drupal module administration page
	 	(<your-site>/admin/build/modules)
	 
	 Choose which option you want to use: 
	 
	 (A) One brand bar for the entire website
	 
		Configure which brand bar you want at the top of the page 
	 	on the NC State Branding Bar Module Settings page
	 	
	 	(<your-site>/admin/settings/ncstatebrandingbar)
	 
	 (B) Different brand bars for the different sections of the website 
	 
	 	Configure which brand bar you want to display on different 
	 	sections of your site via the Block Administration page
	 	
	 	(<your-site>/admin/build/block)
 	
 	
